Files:
  ~/storage/shared/ebooks - Ebooks directory (save epubs here)

Ebook Downloads:
  Library Genesis (libgen.li) - Shadow library with most books:
    1. Search: curl -s "http://libgen.li/index.php?req=<title>" | grep -oP 'ids=[0-9,]+' | head -1
       (or browse: w3m -dump "http://libgen.li/index.php?req=<title>")
    2. Pick a file ID from the ids list
    3. Get info: curl -s "http://libgen.li/json.php?object=f&ids=<id>"
    4. Extract "md5" and "extension" from JSON response
    5. Download: curl -LO "http://libgen.li/get.php?md5=<md5>" -o ~/storage/shared/ebooks/<name>.<ext>
    WARNING: Some ISPs block libgen (e.g., Virgin Media UK). If blocked:
      - Try mirrors: libgen.vg, libgen.bz, libgen.gl
      - Get mirrors: w3m -dump "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Library_Genesis" | grep -E "libgen\.(li|vg|bz|gl)"
      - Use mobile data instead of WiFi

  Project Gutenberg (gutenberg.org) - Free public domain books:
    1. Search: w3m -dump "https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/search/?query=<title>"
    2. Find book ID from URL or results (e.g., book page shows "pg1342" or URL has /ebooks/1342)
    3. Download (use cache URL, NOT ebooks URL):
       curl -sLO "https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/<id>/pg<id>.epub"
       Example: curl -sLO "https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/1342/pg1342.epub"
    4. Move: mv pg<id>.epub ~/storage/shared/ebooks/<title>.epub
    Note: Only public domain works (copyright expired, mostly older books)
    WRONG: https://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/1342.epub.images (this is a redirect page)
    CORRECT: https://www.gutenberg.org/cache/epub/1342/pg1342.epub (direct file)

  Standard Ebooks (standardebooks.org) - Quality public domain:
    1. Search: w3m -dump "https://standardebooks.org/ebooks?query=<title>"
    2. Find book page, look for epub download link
    3. Download: curl -LO "<epub_url>" -o ~/storage/shared/ebooks/<name>.epub

